parameters:
\SE[4]Meow! It's Onee-san!!! \SE[1]You really came to help
me after all...! \SM[double]\SE[35]For me... I'm so
moved...!!

\SE[94]Onee-san said she won't stop, you know.
\!\SE[3]You're the older one here. \!\SE[91]Step away from
the door... It's annoying.
\SE[74]Well... I hope everything will work out somehow...
\SE[2]...Oh? \SE[0]And who might this lovely young lady be?

\SE[6]Oh my, it's the first time we meet! Apparently, there
are three people in the world with the same face. \SE[20]And
besides, I won't forget a cute girl like you who looks like
an older sister.

\SE[2]You must be Laura. You're like a temporary ally, it
seems.

\SE[11]Ms. Laura! I am Cat! \!\SE[25]Please remember me as
Information Broker Cat!

\SE[2]Information Broker-san...? Why is someone like you in
a place like this?

\SE[4]Of course, it's obvious that illegal entry would be
exposed...

\SE[2]This person, huh. She's also a treasure hunter.
\SE[3]She's like a looter who excavates ancient treasures.

\SE[7]So you stepped on a clumsy and foolish trap, and
that's why you're trapped here.

\SE[4]As you can see, I may be a bit of a klutz. \.But I'm
still pretty capable. \!\SE[75]That's why I came all the way
here to help.

\SE[46]Ah...!! Mistress's carrot and stick...! \SE[25]This
cat... gets excited and wet...!!

\SE[20]You're so noisy. \.You're really making things
difficult for me \!\SE[3]...Hmm.\.I'll open it.

\SE[35]Ah...! The fresh air of the outside world...!!
\SE[14]I... I can feel the essence of life again!

\SE[4]Yes, yes... Because escaping is only until we get
outside. \SE[59]So please be quiet until then.

\SE[1]Ah, that's right. \.Before I forget, I'll give this to
Laura-san.

\SE\SE[55]It's Uber Cats!!! \!\SE[55]Please try pressing
that button!

\SE[56]With this, you can do shopping anytime! \SE[15]Say
goodbye to the state of shortage...!!

\SE[123]S-Shopping anytime...!? \.Even if I really received
such an incredible thing!?

\SE[16]Please take it! \!\SE[55]Let's destroy the economy
together...!!

Uber Cats!! has been unlocked. You can now 'shop' anytime
from the menu screen.

Also, please use it in case of emergencies as it also serves
as a 'bug' countermeasure. I hope we won't need it though...

\SE[60]Well, isn't it about time? Let's move forward.
\!\SE[4]This nonsense can be somewhat useful too.
